-- BP Plans to Flare Gases at Carson, California, Refinery Through Oct. 4
-- B y   S a m a n t h a   Z e e
-- 2010-09-30T00:21:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/bp-plans-to-flare-gases-at-carson-california-refinery.html
BP Plc plans to flare gases at its
Carson, California, refinery starting tomorrow and lasting
through Oct. 4, according to a filing with state regulators.  To contact the reporter on this story:
